 -1.0368520021438599], "metadata": {"document_id": "b38b857f-346f-41d4-ab71-2184ce83cc46", "title": "Leave Policy", "department": "HR", "page": 1, "chunk_index": 0, "version": 1, "uploaded_by": "27599f5f-d00d-4aa7-bb10-23fdb6006193", "text": "# Kharesiya Leave Policy\n\n## Overview\nAll full-time employees are entitled to paid leave as per company policy.\n\n## Annual Leave\n- Employees receive 18 days of annual leave per calendar year.\n- Leave must be applied at least 3 working days in advance via the HR portal.\n- Manager approval is required before leave is confirmed.\n\n## Sick Leave\n- Up to 10 sick days per year with medical certificate for absences over 2 consecutive days.\n- Notify your manager before 10:00 AM on the day of absence.\n\n## How to Apply for Leave\n1. Log in to the HR portal at hr.kharesiya.internal\n2. Navigate to Leave Management \u2192 Apply Leave\n3. Select leave type (Annual / Sick / Casual)\n4. Choose dates and add reason\n5. Submit for manager approval\n6. You will receive email confirmation once approved\n\n## Casual Leave"}, "namespace": ""}, "b38b857f-346f-41d4-ab71-2184ce83cc46_1": {"values": [-0.71966552734375, -0.23675833642482758, -3.5575640201568604, -0.06209983304142952, 0.05154586583375931, -0.0771632045507431, 0.3367827534675598, 0.06992782652378082, 1.0822124481201172, -0.8289473056793213, 0.025397159159183502, 0.2908117175102234, 1.0727274417877197, 0.8026817440986633, 0.3218623399734497, -0.05272823944687843, 0.22130075097084045, -1.1549041271209717, -1.5082414150238037, -0.05795492231845856, -0.3393269181251526, 0.00867185927927494, -0.3843168616294861, 0.039193183183670044, 0.7076835632324219, 0.9603315591812134, 0.3964138925075531, 0.392250657081604, 0.17779873311519623, 0.46227532625198364, 0.08051978796720505, 0.8662609457969666, 1.0070648193359375, -0.6992680430412292, 0.835373044013977, -1.6752437353134155, 0.8020210266113281, 0.05535413324832916, -0.029426544904708862, -1.1777435541152954, 1.8172569274902344, -0.00